streaming and starting to post like processes of art has gone down a lot because the overall main goal for me was to find an audience on both to share my stuff with, but with art (and games) it's algorythmically difficult to do so. Maybe I'll reconsider this too but for now...

touch with (if you wanna keep in touch then discord might be the best thing). The account might still exist but I might just browse twitter barely from time to time, however at some point I'll just deactivate it. On the youtube and twitch side the motivation to keep...

post art on and no longer streaming or post animations on youtube (I was planining on doing posting animation there). Here the current situation with the whole No-Freaking-Thankyous but also the toxicity of the platform as a whole make it difficult to continue browsing it and...
